001package org.biopax.paxtools.impl.level3;
002
003import org.biopax.paxtools.model.BioPAXElement;
004import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.CovalentBindingFeature;
005import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.SequenceModificationVocabulary;
006
007
008public class CovalentBindingFeatureImpl extends BindingFeatureImpl implements CovalentBindingFeature
009{
010        private SequenceModificationVocabulary modificationType;
011
012        public CovalentBindingFeatureImpl() {
013        }
014        
015        @Override
016        public Class<? extends CovalentBindingFeature> getModelInterface()
017        {
018                return CovalentBindingFeature.class;
019        }
020
021        public SequenceModificationVocabulary getModificationType()
022        {
023                return this.modificationType;
024        }
025
026        public void setModificationType(SequenceModificationVocabulary modificationType)
027        {
028                this.modificationType = modificationType;
029        }
030
031        @Override
032        protected boolean semanticallyEquivalent(BioPAXElement element)
033        {
034                if(!(element instanceof CovalentBindingFeature))
035                        return false;
036                
037                CovalentBindingFeature that = (CovalentBindingFeature) element;
038                SequenceModificationVocabulary type = that.getModificationType();
039                boolean value = ((type == null) ?
040                                this.getModificationType() == null :
041                                this.getModificationType().equals(type));
042                return value && super.semanticallyEquivalent(element);
043        }
044
045        @Override
046        public int equivalenceCode()
047        {
048                return super.equivalenceCode() +
049                       29 * (modificationType == null ? 0 : modificationType.equivalenceCode());
050        }
051}
